<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>122</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka lunggil gilo buoksa hi,
 Na Temple in suok sakin;
 A sunga hin Aw ka Lalpa,
 Kumkhuon hung cheng zing inla.

[V2]
 Na umna chu (2)
 Kumsawt kipahna a suok.

[V3]
 2. Aw khatvei bek ki mu leng Aw!
 Khatvei bek Nang hun mu leng;
 Khawvel hawihna haw cheng sangin,
 Aleh za'n Nang na hawih zawi.

[V4]
 Kipieng ka ie, (2)
 Nangmah tawh cheng khawm dingin.

[V5]
 3. Aw hawk thielin ka gitlohna,
 Ka thagau hukdam in la;
 Ka chimta ie thima um chu,
 Hung lengin van eng lopi.

[V6]
 Na hung en chun, (2)
 Ka lung kipahna'n a dim.</lyrics>
<title>Kumsawt Kipahna</title>
</song>